## 📊 Performance Impact

### Improvements
- **Stream Delay**: 15ms default (vs instant) - better readability
- **Type Hints**: 100% coverage - better IDE support
- **Configuration**: Local config priority - faster loading

### Memory
- **Themes**: ~2KB additional memory per theme
- **Type Hints**: No runtime impact
- **Configuration**: Minimal JSON loading overhead

## 🔒 Security

### Trust Management
- `/init` command adds directory to trusted list
- Local config respects trust boundaries
- No changes to existing security model

