## Release Notes

**Date**: April 19, 2026
**Version**: 15.0.0
**Codename**: "Professional Polish"

**Highlights**:
- Professional styling system comparable to GitHub Copilot
- Optimal defaults for better UX
- Complete type safety and LSP support
- Hierarchical configuration system
- Hidden commands for power users

**Breaking Changes**:
- Session behavior: New by default (was auto-resume)
- Configuration: Local config takes priority over global

**Migration**: No action required for most users. Power users may want to run `/init` in project directories for local configuration.